# Transport

**Static Property**

A static property that refers to an object that describes the available transport type values.

## Declaration

```swift
static Transport: typeof TransportType;
```

## Discussion

This value allows you to access the [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/TransportType] enumeration with `mapkit.Directions.Transport`.
